    <div class="dms-features">
      <h2>DMS Core Features</h2>
      <div class="features-container">
        <div class="feature-container">
          <h3>Incident Reporting</h3>
          <p>Teachers and staff can submit incident reports electronically, making it easier to keep a detailed record of disciplinary issues and provide administrators with timely information.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-container">
          <h3>Communication and Alerts</h3>
          <p>DMS often include features for sending notifications and alerts to parents, teachers, and administrators regarding disciplinary incidents. This ensures that all stakeholders are aware of the situation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-container">
          <h3>Data Analysis and Reporting</h3>
          <p>DMS can analyze discipline data over time to identify trends and patterns in student behavior. This helps schools make informed decisions and implement preventive measures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-container">
          <h3>Intervention Planning</h3>
          <p>DMS assist in creating intervention plans for students who repeatedly engage in misbehavior. These plans may include counseling, mentoring, or additional support to address the root causes of the behavior.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-container">
          <h3>Documentation and Accountability</h3>
          <p>DMS help in maintaining a detailed and standardized record of disciplinary actions taken, ensuring transparency and accountability in the disciplinary process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-container">
          <h3>Parental Involvement</h3>
          <p>DMS enable better communication with parents or guardians, allowing them to be informed about their child's behavior and any actions taken by the school to address it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-container">
          <h3>Legal Compliance</h3>
          <p>DMS help schools adhere to legal requirements by ensuring that disciplinary actions are in compliance with state and federal laws.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-container">
          <h3>Streamlined Discipline Management</h3>
          <p>Our system simplifies the process of reporting, tracking, and resolving disciplinary incidents, saving schools time and resources.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-container">
          <h3>Comprehensive Documentation</h3>
          <p>Say goodbye to inconsistent record-keeping. Our system maintains a transparent, organized, and comprehensive disciplinary record.</p>
        </div>
